an><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза санаси</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Қарз олувчи банк номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Марказий банкининг Тошкент шаҳар Бош бошқармаси Ҳисоб-китоб-касса марказидаги вакиллик ҳисобварағининг рақами </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ҳисоб-китоб-касса марказидаги вакиллик ҳисоварағининг рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Алоқа манзилгоҳи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Алоқа учун манзил</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон рақами: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Телефон рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Факс рақами: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Факс рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ломбард кредитини олиш санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Ломбард кредитини қайтариш муддати</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">гача бўлган муддатга, йиллик </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Фоиз ставкаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> фоиз ломбард фоиз ставкаси бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Олинадиган кредит миқдори суммаси кўрсатилади</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм миқдорида ломбард кредити беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Кредит суммасини юқорида қайд этилган вакиллик ҳисобварағига ўтказишингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Кредитни таъминлаш учун Ўзбекистон Республика валюта биржасидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Депо ҳисобварағининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-рақамли ДЕПО ҳисобварағимизнинг «Гаровга олинган» (оператори Марказий банк ҳисобланган) бўлимидаги давлат қимматли қоғозларни ўтказамиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Марказий банки томонидан тижорат банкларига қайта молиялаш кредитларини бериш тартиби тўғрисидаги низом талабларига риоя этилганлигини тасдиқлаймиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республика валюта биржасидаги ДЕПО ҳисобварағидан кўчирма нусхаси илова қилинади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Банк вакилининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> _________________________</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">М.Ў.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
